+| FC3 audit/report view | model divergence and hidden-switch status are materialized views derived from genesis + CAS + ChainTape | dashboard/audit_assertions tests |
+| Art. III shielding | prompt template is represented by hash/id only, not raw hidden prompt or private reasoning | shielding/source-grep tests |
