+## §5. Forbidden Paths / Invariants
+
+- NO sequencer admission changes.
+- NO typed transaction variant, schema, signing-domain, or discriminant change.
+- NO model switch at runtime unless it is rejected by audit as a hidden switch.
+- NO global latest model pointer as source of truth.
+- NO model assignment source of truth outside `genesis_report.json` + CAS/tape
