+- NO dashboard/stdout-only proof.
+- NO raw prompt, raw completion, chain-of-thought, or private tool transcript
+  stored in model identity records.
+- NO `f64` / `f32` in model-temperature or money paths.
+- NO batching with G5, G6, G7, WalletBackend, scheduler, or role classifier.
+- NO Gemini requirement under latest Harness unless a future directive changes
+  the audit policy.
