+## §6. Atom Decomposition
+
+| Atom | Surface | Output |
+|---|---|---|
+| G4.2-A | tests first | `tests/constitution_g4_multi_llm.rs` and `tests/constitution_g4_no_hidden_model_switch.rs` fail before implementation |
